code: @Override public Map<String, Future<Path>> getDistributedCacheEntries() {     return distCacheEntries. }

@Override public InputGate getInputGate(int index) {     return inputGates[index]. }
@Override public void acknowledgeCheckpoint(long checkpointId, CheckpointMetrics checkpointMetrics) {     acknowledgeCheckpoint(checkpointId, checkpointMetrics, null). }

@Override public void declineCheckpoint(long checkpointId, Throwable cause) {     checkpointResponder.declineCheckpoint(jobId, executionId, checkpointId, cause). }
